Applications have been invited from eligible candidates for Cybersree software development programme conducted by C-DIT for the State SC development department. The candidates should have a degree in Engineering (IT, CS,Electronics)/ MCA/M.Sc. (Computer science), and should be aged between 22 and 26 years.The training will be held at Cybersree Centre, Thiruvananthapuram.Those selected for the seven-month programme will be given a stipend of Rs.4,500 per month. Applications should be sent to Cybersree, C-DIT, Womenâ€™s College Road, Thycaud, Thiruvananthapuram - 695014 before January 8.